column2: SELECT * FROM(  SELECT  ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY gi.specobjid) AS Row,  gl.h_alpha_flux, gl.h_beta_flux, gl.h_gamma_flux, gl.neiii_#_flux, gl.oiii_#_flux, gl.oiii_#_flux,gl.oi_#_flux, gl.oii_#_flux, gl.oiii_#_flux, gl.nii_#_flux, gl.sii_#_flux,  gl.h_alpha_flux_err, gl.h_beta_flux_err, gl.h_gamma_flux_err, gl.neiii_#_flux_err, gl.oiii_#_flux_err, gl.oiii_#_flux_err,gl.oi_#_flux_err, gl.oii_#_flux_err, gl.oiii_#_flux_err, gl.nii_#_flux_err, gl.sii_#_flux_err  FROM galSpecInfo as gi  JOIN galSpecLine AS gl ON gi.specobjid = gl.specobjid)  AS numTable WHERE numTable.Row BETWEEN # AND #
